Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:16.20,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}もう　大丈夫　信じてジャンプしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:21.72,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}遠く浮かぶ雲　ひとっとびできるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.87,0:23:27.20,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}そんなドキドキ　想像できなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:33.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}みんなの明日の夢　守るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.29,0:23:39.30,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}勇気ありったけ　さあ　握り締めて飛びたて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.24,0:23:45.17,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ひとりじゃ　泣きそうな　大きい空でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.31,0:23:48.48,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}仲間がいれば　笑顔になれる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:51.68,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ホラ　ただ奇跡じゃないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.83,0:23:56.59,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}約束したから　心に決めたから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.73,0:24:00.14,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}逃げないよ　真っ直ぐ立ち向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:09.71,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}もっともっと素敵な世界のために　Over Sky

Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:46.72,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}即使是一個人會想要哭泣的廣闊天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.81,0:22:50.11,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}不要逃避  勇敢面對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.38,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}和夥伴們一起  Over Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:10.39,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}如果連掌心也能夠感受到風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:16.20,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}已經沒問題了  懷著信心起跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:21.72,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}遙遠的浮雲  一飛便能夠便能夠到達
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.87,0:23:27.20,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}那樣的興奮  從來都無法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:33.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}去守護大家明天的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.29,0:23:39.30,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}緊握所有的勇氣起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.24,0:23:45.17,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}即使是一個人會想要哭泣的無垠天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.31,0:23:48.48,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}有同伴在  就會露出笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:51.68,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}看  這並不是什麼奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.83,0:23:56.59,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}因為已經約定  因為已下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.73,0:24:00.14,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}不會逃避  勇敢面對
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:09.71,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}為了更加美好的世界  Over Sky

;Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================================================================================Main

Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  沒米了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但補給都還沒有到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂本姐  米用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒料到一下子人就湊齊了沒儲備這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好需要不少物品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能出去買點回來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了！

Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第 5 話\N「我的羅馬尼亞」


Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  我們準備進行臨時補給
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能開大型卡車的是雪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對羅馬尼亞比較熟悉的是盧基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是這任務就交給你們倆了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶  好久沒有開車了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道敵人什麼時候會攻過來  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法分配太多人手  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜風兜風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也很想去基地外面逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的任務肯定來者不拒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外宮藤和麗奈也一起同行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我還是待機算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  宮藤拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶路就交給你了  盧基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮藤  任務中要服從雪莉的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼有想要什麼東西就說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的訓練道具之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  不指這一類
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家需要補給的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起補給啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好訓練睡個好覺  這是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在訓練後為了保持士氣需要個浴室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的腦袋裡只有訓練了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有點更正常的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我希望要點紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  品茶的時間也是需要的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要台收音機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有台很好用的卡爾斯蘭製通信器了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是放在這裡聽的收音機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家聽下音樂或者新聞不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了  宮藤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅茶和收音機是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴  我要鋼琴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣  鋼琴可是搬不回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想聽薩尼婭彈鋼琴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了薩尼婭  你沒有想要的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉  點你自己要的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴克霍隆呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎  沒什麼特別想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那給克莉絲的禮物之類的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲嗎  也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要可…可愛的…衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我帶件衣服回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服嗎  怎麼樣的比較好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你了  尺寸基本也和你差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得行的東西就可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是機會難得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說不要了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實佩琳她把領的工資和存款都捐給高盧復興財團了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了芳佳  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅茶之外再幫我帶點花的種子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…然後是哈特曼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈特曼那傢伙  還在睡覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床啦  哈特曼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我睡90分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵貴神速  快給我起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去買東西  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼想要的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零食！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所需要的是鬧鐘！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零食！零食！零食！零食！零食！……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  拜託你帶個鬧鐘回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧…鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮藤  枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我買個枕頭回來  我要個枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枕頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整體要黑的最好有些紅色當點綴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面料要是天鵝絨的  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的話就要摸上去手感好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填充物要是水鳥的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽絨或者是小毛片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉  你這麼一股腦說出來我聽的都糊塗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你寫  別弄錯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住了  絕對不准忘了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬要平安回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮  麗奈也一起來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方視野良好  沒有來車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要掉下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:07:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳佳芳佳  到羅馬城了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  芳佳是第一次來羅馬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以前的競技場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是公會堂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳佳就像個孩子似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為羅馬是個歷史悠久的城市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好棒的城市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧基尼生在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在非洲也天天念羅馬好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為的確是個好地方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多數東西這裡都有賣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:08:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收音機就這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把哈特曼的份給忘了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧基尼  這個幫我拿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅茶和花還有洋服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很合身呢  宮藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這是巴克霍隆拜託我買的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要穿這個 ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  這是給她妹妹克莉絲穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣…喘不過來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不是這樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直…不敢想像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧基尼超級飛踢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一腳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恰巧路過的正義夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯卡·盧基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞嗎  多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  那些傢伙是黑手黨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多就是那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:11:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  小路還是很危險的  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心點才行喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  要是去買東西的話一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不是來買東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是來幹什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  觀光吧  或者說散步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為沒出過家門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對羅馬還是不怎麼熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟會對出生的城市不熟悉  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很奇怪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交給我盧基尼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？也不在車裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛還坐在店裡的椅子上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把剩下的錢都給盧基尼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還沒來得及買食材呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她到時候就會回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太壯觀了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧基尼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說像這樣背著身把硬幣扔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就還能再來羅馬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這貓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢包空了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連個影子都沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管到處找人問
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一點頭緒都沒有  都已經累趴了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉  這個好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這個真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個蛋糕再給我一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡從這裡俯瞰下去的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至都不想回家希望一直待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就待在這裡不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:14:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能保護這座美麗的羅馬城嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從房子裡冒出煙來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是準備食物的炊煙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一間間的就是民眾生活的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民眾？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實還有一處風景我很想讓你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可一定要讓我看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.29,0:15:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那麼等下次有機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙都南下到羅馬了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是異型軍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了  宮藤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點逃吧  盧基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  雪莉  在那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在塔上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了  因為我是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個幫我拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔女？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必須要保護羅馬尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧基尼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅馬尼亞由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別衝太前面  盧基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解  但是單獨作戰是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也一樣想保護盧基尼的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  雪莉  芳佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了  聯合攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪莉  看見核心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  X型攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧基尼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  來吧 來吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳佳  這個幫我拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我很想讓你看的景色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧基尼不會…害怕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那麼可怕的敵人戰鬥  不會害怕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不打敗異型軍羅馬尼亞就不復存在了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的魔女就是要保護大家的家園和朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(345,355)\fs17}noblesse oblige
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地位高責任重嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞老是說些難懂的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:18:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人能回去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今真是美妙的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我終於瞭解到我該做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜瑪利亞  再見嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然把置辦糧食的錢用得一乾二淨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監督責任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我也有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起反省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  盧基尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到我說的東西了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到想要的東西了嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給薩尼婭買了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  芳佳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的艾拉的要求太瑣碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉  拜託別人時要稍微節制點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩琳  這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是花的種子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗奈提議不妨在這個基地周圍種上花看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗奈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想讓佩琳教我種花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起種吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:21:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先萬壽菊要種在陽光充足的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的羅馬洋甘菊和香檸檬要避免在夏天受到陽光直射
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零食…零食…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴克霍隆  這個怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部不會太緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼  這個正好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下面有請本日首次公開出席招待會的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅馬尼亞王國第一王女  瑪利亞殿下致辭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日  羅馬受到了異型軍的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因小小的魔女們的勇猛表現異形軍被擊退了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我從她那學到了非常重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護這個世界  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每人應做自己力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也應該盡我所能來保護羅馬尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.73,0:22:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯卡·盧基尼少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.25,0:22:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著深深地謝意 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.93,0:22:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅將這些微不足道的謝禮送給501統合戰鬥航空團的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好重

Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.38,0:24:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩尼婭抱著我買的枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.54,0:24:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩尼婭那纖細的胳膊  胸部  
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.22,0:24:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體溫和心跳都在枕頭上留下痕跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.26,0:24:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  Strike Witches2
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.25,0:24:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比天空更高
